Description:
Ballistics of the 3VOF34 round, with the 3OF43 "Albatross" HE-F shell and the 4-Z-2 full charge, fired from 203mm 2A44 as part of the 2S7 "Pion" and the 2S7M "Malka" self-propelled gun. Loads 43.14 kg of 37/1 tubular grains. 

Per АРТИЛЛЕРИЙСКОЕ ВООРУЖЕНИЕ 2A44 ТЕХНИЧЕСКОЕ ОПИСАНИЕ ИНСТРУКЦИЯ ПО ЭКСПЛУАТАЦИИ (Часть 1) 2A44 TO (К изделию 2С7), develops 3,200 kgf/cm² breech pressure at 15℃. This is converted to piezoelectric value at 1.12 * 0.098. Rifling length is 9550 mm, length of chamber (breech to start of rifling) is 1504 mm, chamber is 63 L.

Per АРТИЛЛЕРИЙСКИЕ МЕТАТЕЛЬНЫЕ ЗАРЯДЫ, performance varies:
Temp. Pmcp   m.v. [copper crusher gauge]
      MPa    m/s
-50°  261.93 920   
 15°  313.92 960
 50°  324.93 973
